summary: A uunp bodyslide preset where I attempted to create good cleavage on outfits. OUTDATED - I recommend use of my newer bodyslide presets.
descriptionHtml:
A BodySlide Preset with good cleavage. OUTDATED - I recommend use of my other bodyslide presets.

[size=3][b]Requires:[/b][/size] BodySlide and Outfit Studio, HDT physics, XP32 Skeleton extended, realistic rag-dolls and force.

The character used is - [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/85199/?]Amelia Rose[/url] - my personal racemenu preset .
The ENB is Grim and Somber - Azura.

[size=3][b]Installation:[/b][/size]
[list=1]
[*]Download and extract
[*]Go to Skyrim>>Data>>CalienteTools>>BodySlide>>SliderPresets>>(put the file in here!)
[*]Start BodySlide program, select this body from among the UUNP hdt presets, batch build, done!
[/list]
author: wnisewond
